    "Other studies evaluate LLMs for annotating sentiment in free-text patient survey comments (43).",
    "There is also emerging interest in applying sentiment analysis to patient-provider communications or clinical notes, although privacy remains a key consideration.",
    "The goal is often to gain actionable insights that can lead to better quality of care and improved patient outcomes (63).",
    "Sentiment analysis helps understand how health information and misinformation spread and are received within the complex modern information environment (9).",
